# Maintain Test Report

After any code change:

1. Read `tests/acceptance_tests.md`.
2. Create or update `tests/test_report.md`.
3. Keep a simple Markdown table with one row for every acceptance test plus one extra row for the overall unit test suite.
4. Each row must include: `ID`, `Line Item`, `Description`, `Result`, and `Notes`.
5. Valid results are `Pass`, `Fail`, `Not Run`, or `Blocked`. Never mark a test `Pass` unless it was actually executed.
6. If a test was not executed, explain why in `Notes`.
